    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Mustura daral, a and d. MUMF 18065, 62.5 mm SL, male; lip structure and head with suborbital flap. Scale bar= 1mm; b–c. MUMF 18068, 56.7 mm SL, male; air bladder and intestine; e. MUMF 18064, 66.8 mm SL, male; pectoral fin. Vertical scale bar = 1 mm. t represents tubercles in the Figure; f. MUMF 18075, 70.4 mm SL, female; pectoral fin." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500982/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

